PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the OCHAPOWACE BAND, of some 323 hectares of land situated in the Rural Municipality of Kingsley No. 124, near Broadview, Saskatchewan, all mines and minerals included, together with all the mines and minerals existing within another 0.445 hectares and all the mines and minerals, other than coal or petroleum, existing within another 1.084 hectares, all as Ochapowace Indian Reserve No. 71-87.
